invalid type: string "VIT Hostels \nCode of Conduct \nSL. \nNO.  NATURE OF MISCONDUCT ACTION TO BE TAKEN* \n1. \nViolations of Hostel Etiquette \na) Avoiding giving attendance in the Hostel \nbeing present in the night \n1st Time: Warning \n2nd time: Outing Cancellation for 15 days \nOn Repetition: Outing Cancellation for one semester \nb) Entering Campus Gate / Hostel Block Gate \nring the examin